# Clean product URLs: /memorials/<slug> serves memorial.html.
#
# The destination MUST be the clean form `/memorial` (not `/memorial.html`).
# Cloudflare Pages applies `.html` canonicalisation to rewrite targets — if
# we point at `/memorial.html` the edge 308-redirects the browser to
# `/memorial`, which strips the `:slug` and breaks the page. Using the
# clean URL keeps the response a true rewrite (status 200, address bar
# unchanged) so memorial.html can read the slug from the path.
#
# Do NOT add a `/memorial -> /memorials` redirect: memorial.html already
# handles the "no slug" case gracefully by showing "Product not found".
/memorials/:slug   /memorial   200
